T02D1517:35b-0: @35b * // rkang pa bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad pa bsgyur ba'i bstod pa bzhugs so//
T02D1517:35b-2: # // dpal rdo rje mkha' 'gro dpa' bo chen po dpa'
T02D1517:35b-3: bo'i dbang phyug / sa gsum bskyod cing g-yo bar
T02D1517:35b-5: mche ba gtsigs pa 'jigs su rung ba 'jigs par mdzad pa /
T02D1517:35b-6: spyan brgya stong phrag mnga' ba /
T02D1517:35b-8: keng rus kyi phreng bas brgyan pa'i sku can /
T02D1517:35b-10: 'bar bas kun nas skor bas reg pa /
T02D1517:35b-11: dgra sta dang zhags pa dang dpal can 'phyar ba /
T02D1517:35b-12: bskal pa'i mtha'i du ba drag po'i sku can /
T02D1517:35b-13: rnam par gtsigs pa'i zhal ha ha sgrogs pa /
T02D1517:35b-14: ma mo'i tshogs kyis yongs su bskor ba'i sngags can /
T02D1517:35b-15: lhan cig skyes ma'i mdzes ma dang gcugs par mdzad pa /
T02D1517:35b-16: h'um h'um zhes sgrogs pa'i zhal can /
T02D1517:35b-17: ngur khrod chen po la dbyes pa /
T02D1517:35b-18: 'byung po thams cad kun du skrag par mdzad pa //
T02D1517:35b-19: bskal pa'i mtha' ma'i me'i gzi brjid can /
T02D1517:35b-20: ral pa'i tshogs kyi cod pa na /
T02D1517:35b-21: khri rkang dang thod pa dang gsal zhing gis phug pa 'dzin pa /
T02D1517:35b-22: rgya mtsho chen po'i ske rags can /
T02D1517:35b-23: stag gi pags pa'i na bza' 'tshang ba /
T02D1517:35b-24: ro langs kyi tshogs 'joms par mdzad pa /
T02D1517:35b-25: bgegs chen po las skyob pa po //
T02D1517:35b-26: dgra la nges par gnod pa mdzad pa /
T02D1517:35b-27: stong gsum gyi stong chen po ba spu 'khyil pa gcig gi nang du gnas pa po //
T02D1517:35b-28: zhal brgya phrag stong mnga' ba /
T02D1517:35b-29: ye shes kyi rgya mtsho'i zhal can /
T02D1517:35b-30: sha chen po dang khrag dang zhag gsol ba po //
T02D1517:35b-31: bdud thams cad kyi stobs 'joms pa po //
T02D1517:35b-32: 'byin pa dang sdud pa mdzad pa po //
T02D1517:35b-33: klu thams cad skems pa dang /
T02D1517:35b-37: ri rab g-yo gar byed pa'i sgra can /
T02D1517:35b-39: go skabs chen po'i thig le'i bdag nyid can /
T02D1517:35b-40: sangs rgyas bye ba stong skad cig gis rdzogs par mdzad pa /
T02D1517:35b-41: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs pa /
T02D1517:35b-42: las thams cad rab tu 'jug par mdzad pa //
T02D1517:35b-44: rnam par rtog pa thams cad 'joms par mdzad pa /
T02D1517:35b-45: mgo bos 'khrigs pas reg pa'i sku can /
T02D1517:36a-2: srung ba chen po byed pa /
T02D1517:36a-3: sdang ba rnams kyi rnam par 'joms pa po //
T02D1517:36a-5: khro bo spro zhing spro bar byed du 'jug pa /
T02D1517:36a-6: dbang po'i dra ba sems can thams cad kyi bdag nyid can /
T02D1517:36a-9: rab tu rtsod pa'i blo gros chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1517:36a-10: rkang pa bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad pa'i bstod pa'o //
T02D1517:36a-11: shr'i dza ya se n'a dang /
T02D1517:36a-12: dpal dar ma yon tan gyis bsgyur ro //
T02D1517:36a-13: 'di la tshigs su bcad par bsgyur pa'ang snang ngo //
T02D1517:36a-14: dge ba 'di yis nye bar mtshon nas ni //
T02D1517:36a-15: sems can rnams kyis dus gsum bsags pa yi //
T02D1517:36a-16: zag bcas zag med zung 'jug dge ba rnams //
T02D1517:36a-17: bla med byang chub chen por bsngo bar bgyi //
